languages.text: "Все отдадим, не пожалеем! В любую драку готовы, за правое дело всепострадаем и искупим! За Императора и Вашу Светлость! Только не губите и с Футфола не гоните!"

"We'll give it our all and hold nothing back! We'll join any fight for the righteous cause, to redempt ourselves with hardship and endeaviour! For the Emperor and Your {mf|Lord|Lady}ship! Just don't banish us from Footfall or vanish us altogether!"

languages.text: “我们会全力以赴，绝不退所！我们愿意为了正义，加入各种各样的战斗，通过我们的努力与来赎还！为了帝皇！为了大人您！只求您不要把我们赶出落脚港，也不要把我们彻底消灭！”
languages.original_text: "We'll give it our all and hold nothing back! We'll join any fight for the righteous cause, to redempt ourselves with hardship and endeaviour! For the Emperor and Your {mf|Lord|Lady}ship! Just don't banish us from Footfall or vanish us altogether!"

traits.speaker: NewPirateVendor

languages.text: 「私達は何もためらわず、全力を尽くします！困難と努力で自らを贖うために、すべての正義の元に行われる戦に参加します！皇帝、そして陛下の為に！なので、私達をフットフォールから追放したり、消したりしないでください！」
languages.original_text: "We'll give it our all and hold nothing back! We'll join any fight for the righteous cause, to redempt ourselves with hardship and endeaviour! For the Emperor and Your {mf|Lord|Lady}ship! Just don't banish us from Footfall or vanish us altogether!"

languages.text: «¡Lo daremos todo y no nos guardaremos nada! ¡Nos uniremos a cualquier lucha por la causa justa para redimirnos con penurias y esfuerzos! ¡Por el Emperador y por mi{mf|lord|lady}! ¡Lo único que le pido es que no nos destierre de Paso o se deshaga de nosotros!»
languages.original_text: "We'll give it our all and hold nothing back! We'll join any fight for the righteous cause, to redempt ourselves with hardship and endeaviour! For the Emperor and Your {mf|Lord|Lady}ship! Just don't banish us from Footfall or vanish us altogether!"

traits.speaker: NewPirateVendor

languages.text: "Wir geben alles und halten nichts zurück! Wir schließen uns jedem Kampf für die rechtschaffene Sache an, um uns zu reh-haar-filetieren! Für den Imperator und Euer {mf|Lord|Lady}schaft! So lange Ihr uns nur nicht von Footfall verbannt ... oder verbrennt!"
languages.original_text: "We'll give it our all and hold nothing back! We'll join any fight for the righteous cause, to redempt ourselves with hardship and endeaviour! For the Emperor and Your {mf|Lord|Lady}ship! Just don't banish us from Footfall or vanish us altogether!"

traits.speaker: NewPirateVendor

languages.text: « On donnera tout ce qu'on a ! On se battra pour la bonne cause et on reculera devant aucun effort pour expirer nos fautes ! Pour l'Empereur et Votre Seigneurie ! Tout ce qu'on vous demande, c'est de pas nous bannir de Castel ou nous massacrer ! »
languages.original_text: "We'll give it our all and hold nothing back! We'll join any fight for the righteous cause, to redempt ourselves with hardship and endeaviour! For the Emperor and Your {mf|Lord|Lady}ship! Just don't banish us from Footfall or vanish us altogether!"

languages.text: "Elimizden ayağımızdan ne gelirse yapacağız! Haklı davanız için saflarınızda çarpışacağız! Gurtuluşa ermek için hayret göstereceğiz! Yaşasın İmparator, yaşasın {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri! Yeter ki bizi Binliman'dan kovmayın, sürgün etmeyin!"
languages.original_text: "We'll give it our all and hold nothing back! We'll join any fight for the righteous cause, to redempt ourselves with hardship and endeaviour! For the Emperor and Your {mf|Lord|Lady}ship! Just don't banish us from Footfall or vanish us altogether!"
